#comments
  %h2.comments-header
  комментарии (
  %span.js-comments-count 
  = item.comments.count
  )
  %ul.hentry
    %li.comment_holder.vote_holder
      .msg-meta
        - if item.comments.empty?
          Нет комментариев для показа.
        - else
          - for comment in item.comments
            %ul.menu.info.author.hcardo
              %li.fn.nickname.username
                - if @discourse.assigner
                  = link_to comment.author,comment.author
              %li.date
                = comment.created_at(:forum_long_ago)
            %div
              = comment.content
Добавить комментарий
- form_for [item, Comment.new()] do |f|
  = f.error_messages
  %p
    = f.label  'Сообщение'
    %br/
    = f.text_area :content
  %p= f.submit
